Presave & Preadd the hell out of this 🫶🏼
➡️ Link is in my bio!!

Sean Riley was a Sherrif Deputy in Wayne County IL 
(My Hometown Area) 
One morning Sean responded to a call on Interstate 64 thinking he was going to give his assistance to someone who was broke down!  Moments after Officer Riley arrived, his life was tragically taken from him by the man he was there to help! 

Sean was a father, husband, son, & loved by so many and was simply at the wrong place at the wrong time and paid the ultimate sacrifice!! 

I wrote this song not only for Sean’s family & friends 
But for all of our men and women who wake up everyday put on that badge and risk their lives to protect us!! 

At the end of the day they have a job to do, but police are people too!! LETS BLOW THIS UP YALL! 🔥
